        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/marrakesh/_scene_python.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9a49e606-9fc8-45bb-aff7-fa4e2a5eee62).Image",
        "Description": "The underbelly of Marrakesh is ablaze due to the war between mobster Tayyb Shadid and drug trafficking powercouple, Hollie Shaw and Jewel Burgeouis.\rZaki Diab, the fortuneteller, has told the couple about secrets that his client Shadid revealed to him, and now the two are preparing to make all of that public, uncaring for others that may be exposed.\rOther players contracted us to discreetly eliminate all parties involved, in a window of less than 10 minutes, in order to close this business.",
